org.cytoscape.cyGraph.algorithms.api
Interface DijkstraResult

public interface DijkstraResult

Provides methods to access get shortest path from source CyNode to other CyNodes, distance, etc. as computed by Dijkstra's algorithm.

Author:
Jimmy
